name: B3
body:
### Welcome to B3

B3 is a [Backbone.js](http://backbonejs.org) starter theme for [WordPress](http://wordpress.org).

It is designed as a launchpad for your own cutting edge themes: so clone it, rename it, hack it and republish it.

### Credits

B3 is developed in Portugal by Lu√≠s Rodrigues (@goblindegook) and Pedro Cruz (@pcruz7).
